<para id="element-27">
(ii) Velocity at the ground
</para>
<para id="element-28">We can find the velocity at the time of strike with ground by calculating component velocities at that instant in the two mutually perpendicular directions and finding the resultant (composite) velocity as :
</para>
<para id="element-29">
<m:math display="block">
