<m:mn> 8 </m:mn>
<m:mspace width="2pt"/>
<m:mi> s </m:mi>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>

</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-49">Neglecting negative value of time, T = 8 s.
</para>
<para id="element-50">
(ii) Horizontal distance, R
</para>
<para id="element-51">
There is no acceleration in horizontal direction. Using equation for uniform motion,
</para>
<para id="element-52">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
