</m:msqrt>
<m:mspace width="2pt"/>
<m:mi> m </m:mi>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>

</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-56">
(iii) Maximum height, H
</para>
<para id="element-57">The maximum height is the sum of the height of the building (
<m:math>
<m:msub>
<m:mi> H </m:mi>
<m:mn> 2 </m:mn>
</m:msub>
</m:math>
) and the height attained by the projectile above the building (
<m:math>
<m:msub>
<m:mi> H </m:mi>
<m:mn> 1 </m:mn>
</m:msub>
</m:math>
). 
 </para>
<para id="element-58"><m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:mi> H </m:mi>
<m:mo> = </m:mo>
<m:msub>
<m:mi> H </m:mi>
<m:mn> 1 </m:mn>
</m:msub>
<m:mo> + </m:mo>
<m:msub>
<m:mi> H </m:mi>
<m:mn> 2 </m:mn>
</m:msub>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-59">We consider vertical motion to find the height attained by the projectile above the building (
<m:math>
<m:msub>
<m:mi> H </m:mi>
<m:mn> 1 </m:mn>
</m:msub>
</m:math>
). 
</para>
<para id="element-60"><m:math display="block">
  <m:mrow>
    <m:msub>
      <m:mi>H</m:mi>
      <m:mn>1</m:mn>
    </m:msub>
    <m:mo>=</m:mo>
    <m:mfrac>
      <m:mrow>
        <m:msup>
          <m:mi>u</m:mi>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
        </m:msup>
        <m:msup>
        <m:mi>sin</m:mi>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
        </m:msup>

        <m:mi>θ</m:mi>
      </m:mrow>
      <m:mrow>
        <m:mn>2</m:mn>
        <m:mi>g</m:mi>
      </m:mrow>
    </m:mfrac>
  </m:mrow>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-61"><m:math display="block">
  <m:mrow>
    <m:mo>⇒</m:mo>
    <m:msub>
      <m:mi>H</m:mi>
      <m:mn>1</m:mn>
    </m:msub>
    <m:mo>=</m:mo>
    <m:mfrac>
      <m:mrow>
        <m:msup>
          <m:mfenced>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mn>40</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
          </m:mfenced>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
        </m:msup>
        <m:msup>
        <m:mi>sin</m:mi>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
        </m:msup>
        <m:msup>
          <m:mn>30</m:mn>
          <m:mn>0</m:mn>
        </m:msup>
      </m:mrow>
      <m:mrow>
        <m:mn>2</m:mn>
        <m:mi>X</m:mi>
        <m:mn>10</m:mn>
      </m:mrow>
    </m:mfrac>
  </m:mrow>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-62"><m:math display="block">
  <m:mrow>
    <m:mo>⇒</m:mo>
    <m:msub>
      <m:mi>H</m:mi>
      <m:mn>1</m:mn>
    </m:msub>
    <m:mo>=</m:mo>
    <m:mfrac>
      <m:mrow>
        <m:msup>
          <m:mfenced>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mn>40</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
          </m:mfenced>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
        </m:msup>
        <m:mi>X</m:mi>
